{"tid":793842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[亞運]韓國教練賽前偷走港將釘鞋 陳佩琦不適應慢0.03秒僅僅出局","createTime":"2018-08-25T17:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T04:24:49.000Z","uid":202348,"like":13,"dislike":176,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"187644bfe90ce0d3ef1eb739b431f7de91b25e08","tid":793842,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:04:17.000Z","msg":"「我好蠢，好大意，真的好蠢。」賽後陳佩琪雙眼通紅，說着事發經過時帶點激動、內疚、混亂，但話語中亦帶點自嘲。<br />\n<br />\n開賽前約半小時，陳佩琪在第二報到室發現釘鞋不在袋內，立即心急如焚，一口氣跑回第一報到室「地毯式」搜索，也沒有發現。陳佩琪說：「所以我再跑到熱身區，但怎樣找也沒有，結果再跑回賽場。有韓國跑手前來問好，溝通後才得知她的教練意外地拿走我的釘鞋，但那刻教練已不在場。」幾經波折，陳佩琪跑了400米搜尋鞋，總算「人間有情」，獲其他跑手借出同碼數的釘鞋上陣，最終以11.97秒，僅僅出局。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/010115_18b60581d7c8e16426370ec1bfdf3ca6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F010115_18b60581d7c8e16426370ec1bfdf3ca6.png&h=6eb164d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時體育/227357/亞運會-2018-陳佩琦失鞋兼出局-港隊三飛人跑入百米準決賽\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2F227357%2F%E4%BA%9E%E9%81%8B%E6%9C%83-2018-%E9%99%B3%E4%BD%A9%E7%90%A6%E5%A4%B1%E9%9E%8B%E5%85%BC%E5%87%BA%E5%B1%80-%E6%B8%AF%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%89%E9%A3%9B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%91%E5%85%A5%E7%99%BE%E7%B1%B3%E6%BA%96%E6%B1%BA%E8%B3%BD&d=VtFwc5N7gImy1hdKMBpwrI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8a5295f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時體育/227357/亞運會-2018-陳佩琦失鞋兼出局-港隊三飛人跑入百米準決賽</a><br />\n<br />\n泡狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCredit to 古巨基巴打"},{"pid":"baa48215722b20b2b6132a2ec78443d499ba3cc7","tid":793842,"uid":15815,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:06:14.000Z","msg":"冇得睇live <br />\n垃圾有線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" cl